definitions.definition: ( chiefly uncountable ) The meat of a pig.
examples: The cafeteria serves pork on Tuesdays.

definitions.definition: ( US politics , slang , derogatory ) Funding proposed or requested by a member of Congress for special interests or their constituency as opposed to the good of the country as a whole.
( MLE , slang , collective ) law enforcement , those who side with criminal prosecution
